courses.title: Vizualizacija kompleksnih stevil
courses.description: Kaj so kompleksna in realna stevila ? Izdelajte preprosto vizualizacijo...
courses.content: # ITS server app [![JavaScript Style Guide](https://img.shields.io/badge/code_style-standard-brightgreen.svg)](https://standardjs.com) ![Heroku](https://heroku-badge.herokuapp.com/?app=rd-its) View REST API documentation [here](https://stoplight.io/p/docs/gh/bartolomej/its-server). ## Setup To install and work on ITS run: 1. `git clone https://github.com/bartolomej/its-server` 2. `cd its-server` 3. `npm install` 4. [configure environment variables](https://www.npmjs.com/package/dotenv#usage) 5. `npm run test-data` 6. `npm start`
